Class MILPModel2TextUtilsYALMIP

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.gatech.mbse.transformations.sysml2milp.utils.MILPModel2TextUtilsYALMIP
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MILPModel2TextUtils

    public class MILPModel2TextUtilsYALMIP
extends java.lang.Object
implements MILPModel2TextUtils
    Collection of utilities for generating a textual representation of a MILP problem in YALMIP / Matlab syntax.

    This is the only file that should produce YALMIP-specific output.

    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Sebastian

      • generatePostamble

        public java.lang.String generatePostamble(java.lang.String visualizationOuput,
                                 int numSolutions,
                                 boolean testingMode)
        Description copied from interface: MILPModel2TextUtils
        Generate postamble.

        Typically, this will include some visualization output, call the solver (or configure it) and generate code that will produce n solutions as specified. The last argument refers to whether or not the required output (Excel data and instanceData) is to be produced, or just the output for the testing infrastructure.

        Specified by:

      • generateExcelOutput

        private java.lang.String generateExcelOutput()
        Generates Matlab code that will generate an excel spreadsheet showing the solution.

        Note that this function is NOT generic and very specific to Matlab! This should be considered a temporary "hack" until a correspondence model can be implemented.
        Returns:
        A set of MATLAB specific commands to generate the required Excel output.
